        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This snare consists of a hidden canister of caltrops attached to a trip wire. When the snare is triggered, it flings the caltrops into either the snare's square or a square adjacent to the snare. You choose which square when you set up the snare.   \nIf the caltrops scatter into the same square as a creature, that creature must attempt the Acrobatics check immediately.",
        "level": 1,
